Package com.ibm.team.process.common.advice

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAdvisorDeclaration
    Static representation of an advisor which is configured for an advisable operation.
    IAdvisorInfo
    An advisor info reports information for an operation advisor.
    IAdvisorInfoCollector
    Report info collector which can create new infos for an operation advisor.
    IAdvisorReport
    A report which encapsulates the result of executing an operation advisor.
    IItemsResponse
    Operation response which carries a collection of persisted items (IItem).
    IObjectsResponse
    Operation response which carries a collection of data transfer objects (EObject).
    IOperationConfigurationInfo
    An operation configuration info provides enough information for the server process to determine if an operation configuration is correct for a given time and place.
    IOperationReport
    A report which encapsulates the result of advising and possibly executing an operation.
    IParticipantDeclaration
    Static representation of a operation participant which is configured for an advisable operation.
    IParticipantReport
    A report which encapsulates the result of executing an operation participant.
    IProcessConfigurationSource
    A process configuration source provides enough information for a server process to determine if a process configuration is correct for a given time and place.
    IProcessReport
    A report for an element of the process runtime, including operations, advisors, and participants.
    IReportInfo
    A report info reports information for an operation, operation advisor, or operation participant.
    IReportInfoCollector
    Collector which is passed to implementors of operation advisors and participants.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvisableOperation
    An operation advisable by process.
    ProcessRunnable
    Runnable which is executed by the Process framework without support for advisors and participants, but which can return an operation report.
    ProjectOperation
    An operation which is governed by a project area.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TeamOperationCanceledException
    Exception which is thrown when an operation is cancelled by process.
